<article class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1>About CalcWise</h1>

  <p>CalcWise is a free online calculator platform designed to help you make quick, accurate calculations across a wide range of categories — from finance and math to health and beyond.</p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>We believe that everyone deserves access to reliable, easy-to-use calculation tools. Whether you're figuring out your monthly mortgage payment, calculating a tip, checking your BMI, or solving a math problem, CalcWise is here to help — no sign-up required, no fees, no hassle.</p>

  <h2>What We Offer</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Finance Calculators:</strong> Mortgage, loan, compound interest, investment, retirement, debt payoff, salary, and savings goal calculators.</li>
    <li><strong>Math Calculators:</strong> Percentage, fraction, area, circumference, and exponent calculators.</li>
    <li><strong>Health Calculators:</strong> BMI, calorie, and body fat percentage calculators.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Approach</h2>
  <p>Every calculator on CalcWise is built with accuracy and simplicity in mind. We provide:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Instant results</strong> — calculations happen in real-time as you type</li>
    <li><strong>Educational content</strong> — formulas and explanations below each calculator</li>
    <li><strong>Mobile-friendly design</strong> — works great on any device</li>
    <li><strong>No registration</strong> — just visit and calculate</li>
  </ul>

  <p>CalcWise is constantly growing. We're always adding new calculators and improving existing ones. If you have a suggestion for a calculator you'd like to see, we'd love to hear from you.</p>
</article>
